{"tid":1670432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"是日最大風向：支持加泰民主並不代表支持加泰獨立！","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:48:56.000Z","uid":167548,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed9bb0373d7ec2496041701e37114ac9a8a3190","tid":1670432,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時連登仔恥笑班飯民左膠天真嬌,<br />\n共產黨眼中普選自治就是獨立, <br />\n大聲屌左膠唔好自欺欺人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解你地做返當年柒過嘅事, <br />\n支持加泰民主並不代表支持加泰獨立！<br />\n共產黨用緊一招名為置之死地而後生, <br />\n就是逼你地宣揚兩個絕境,<br />\n<br />\n支持加泰民主=賭獨立思潮未成形=提早潛意識劃分獨立與民主, 進行內部分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持加泰獨立=直接擋曬美國掐手嘅藉口/美國需時重新部署=香港人再等多次國會準備新對策<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨派啊 獨派啊&hellip; 坐著食花生等好戲唔撚得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直情冷處理成件事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c902736d6b31ff3b310b63754d96f8287770a9c6","tid":1670432,"uid":5627,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caCxF6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaCxF6x.jpg&h=c4418fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"005743305cc9f0aac75adbf00f5c198399f58b03","tid":1670432,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"【加泰集會】支持加泰民主！ = 反對香港獨立！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670368</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c8226d7be2400213f8056666836e6ed54a2c1db","tid":1670432,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa3274d6d78f5968c5dc597679b3616866bdf5","tid":1670432,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":